{
  "texts": [
    "This pattern involves the use of machine learning and cognitive methods to discern meaningful entities within unstructured content, spanning images, videos, audio, text, or other forms of data.",
    "The Recognition Pattern stands as a testament to the capabilities of machine learning, particularly deep learning, in enhancing accuracy and expanding the range of applications in diverse recognition tasks.",
    "Goal-driven system patterns leverage the power of reinforcement learning and other machine learning techniques to equip systems with the ability to simulate scenarios, address recurring problems, and provide real-time offers and auction bids.",
    "Although not as widely used as other patterns, it is rapidly gaining traction due to its potential to be applied to learning through experience and trial and error.",
    "Goal-oriented system patterns contribute to the evolving landscape of AI implementation with a focus on experiential learning and optimal solutions."
  ]
}